Describe a person who likes to dress fashionably
- who he/she is
- what job he/she does
- what kind of dresses he/she wears
- explain why he/she likes fashion

I’d like to talk about my friend An, who is one of the most fashionable people I know.

She is 20 years old and currently a university student. I first met her about six years ago when we were studying together in Ho Chi Minh City. From the very beginning, she stood out because of her stylish appearance and confident personality.

In terms of her style, she always dresses very well and pays a lot of attention to her outfits. She has a great sense of fashion and knows how to mix and match different types of clothing, from casual wear to more formal outfits. She also likes to wear accessories such as earrings, bracelets, or watches to complete her look.

I think one of the reasons why she enjoys fashion so much is that she sees it as a way to express herself. She once told me that dressing well helps her feel more confident and leaves a good impression on others. In addition, she often keeps up with the latest trends by following fashion pages online, which helps her stay updated.

Another thing I really admire about her is that she always dresses appropriately for different occasions. Whether she is going to school, attending an event, or hanging out with friends, she always chooses outfits that suit the situation perfectly.

Overall, I really admire her sense of style, and whenever I need fashion advice, she is always the first person I turn to.
